Titolo: Bullet Girls

Anno: 2014

Descrizione: Bullet Girls (バレットガールズ, Baretto Gāruzu) is a third-person shooter video game for the PlayStation Vita developed by Shade and published by D3 Publisher. The game is an action shooter video game, and has been compared to paintball by Gematsu and Senran Kagura by Siliconera. Bullet Girls takes place in a school that serves upper class girls, and focuses on the Ranger Club, whose members undertake military missions in their spare time. Noted for its ample amounts of ecchi and fanservice content, Bullet Girls game was released on August 21, 2014, in Japan. A sequel, titled Bullet Girls 2, was released on April 21, 2016. A third game, titled Bullet Girls Phantasia for PS4 and PS Vita was released in August 2018 and for PC through Steam on Jan 16, 2020.

Genere: Non specificato


Valutazione: N/A
